		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_UNIT_IGA_NINJA_STRATEGY">
			<Text>The Ninja is a Scout replacement, available only to Iga. It is a superb unit for exploration and espionage; it gains double [ICON_MOVES] Movement in Forest, Jungle and Hills tiles, and can infiltrate rival territory without open borders. Unlike the Scout, the Ninja is slightly more expensive and fights as a ranged unit with a range of 1 hex.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_UNIT_HELP_IGA_NINJA">
			<Text>Excellent at exploration and intelligence-gathering, this Iga Unique Unit replaces the Scout. It gains double [ICON_MOVES] Movement when traversing rough terrain, and can enter rival territory without open borders. Fights as a short-range ranged unit.</Text>
		</Row>
